  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Our customers want their new product to be the way they expect it to be, which is why you need to make sure that the grade displayed on your offer matches the grade of the product the customer is receiving. Otherwise, you expose yourself to a high return rate and poor customer satisfaction. <br><br>To help you ensure your grading fits our customer&#39;s expectations we have designed a toolkit with detailed guidelines for each grade of smartphones / tablets as well as MacBooks / laptops and newly added guidelines for Smartwatches.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Smartphones and Tablets</span></h2>\n<div id=\"BlockWrapper\">\n<div>\n<div id=\"BlockActions\"></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Grade</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Body</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Screen</strong></span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Mint</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Like new. No scratches.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Like new. No scratches.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches visible from a distance of 20cm/8 in (a bit longer than a standard-sized pencil).</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good condition. No scratches visible from a distance of 50 cm/20 in (about an arm&#39;s length).</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good condition. Light but plainly visible scratches.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good condition. Scratches that may be slightly visible when the screen is on.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Stallone</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair condition. Visible signs of use, with scratches and/or dents that can be felt.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair condition. Scratches that may be slightly visible when the screen is on.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">MacBooks/iMacs, Laptops, and Desktop Computers</span></h2>\n<div id=\"BlockWrapper\">\n<div>\n<div id=\"BlockActions\"></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Grade</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Body</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Screen</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Keyboard/Touchpad</strong></span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Mint</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Like new. No scratches. No sticker marks.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Like new. No scratches.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Like new. No scratches or signs of use.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches visible from a distance of 20 cm/8 in (a bit longer than a standard-sized pencil). No sticker marks.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches or signs of use.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good condition. No scratches visible from a distance of 50 cm/20 in (about an arm&#39;s length). No sticker marks.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good condition. No scratches.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good condition. Light scratches or minimal signs of use.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good condition. Light but plainly visible scratches. For desktops and iMacs, plainly visible scratches on the bottom of the device. No sticker marks but decoloration is acceptable.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good condition. No scratches visible when the screen is on.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good condition. Light scratches or minimal signs of use.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Stallone</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair condition. Visible signs of use, with scratches and/or dents that can be felt. No sticker marks but decoloration is acceptable.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair condition. Light scratches that are invisible once the screen is on.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair condition. Visible signs of use, with scratches and/or dents that can be felt.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2></h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Smart Watches</span></h2>\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Grade</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Body</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Screen</strong></span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Mint</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Like new. No scratches.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Like new. No scratches.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches visible from a distance of 20cm/8 in (a bit longer than a standard-sized pencil).</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Excellent condition. No scratches.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good condition. No scratches visible from a distance of 50 cm/20 in (about an arm&#39;s length).</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good condition. No scratches visible when the screen is on.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair condition. May have visible signs of use, with scratches and/or dents that can be felt.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good condition. No scratches visible when the screen is on.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Stallone</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair condition. Visible signs of use, with scratches and/or dents that can be felt.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good condition. No scratches visible when the screen is on.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Other Products</span></h2>\n<div id=\"BlockWrapper\">\n<div>\n<div id=\"BlockActions\"></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Grade</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Description</strong></span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Mint</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">No trace of use.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Very good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">A few traces of use, but they’re invisible from more than 20 cm away.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">A few traces of use, but they’re invisible from more than 50 cm away.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Fair</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">A few traces of use visible from more than 50 cm away, but there’s no obstacle to use.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Stallone</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Marked traces of use, but there’s no obstacle to use.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"BlockWrapper\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Please note: Engravings are not permitted on products graded Premium, Excellent (Mint &amp; Very Good), or Good. For products in Fair &amp; Stallone grade, engravings are allowed provided the text does not contain:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Personal data</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Discriminatory content</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Hate speech</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Obscene material</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Any other inappropriate messages</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The presence of such engraving does not void the customer&#39;s right of withdrawal.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">As a reminder, customers have until the end of the withdrawal period to claim a physical appearance grade that has not been respected. You will then have to propose to the customer a commercial gesture (see table below), an exchange of the product, or the refund if they wish it (withdrawal period). We only display 3 grades to our customers (excluding Premium) while you can list the products into 5 esthetical states.</span></p>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">It is important to note that when in doubt it is always better to choose the lesser grade of two as it is economically damaging to over-grade products (for iPhones ). You can find a one-pager with the detail of the costs of over-grading attached at the bottom of this article.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>NEW</strong>: </span><br><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Here are the fees that may be withheld in the event of a grade not corresponding to the order:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Grade ordered</span></h2>\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Grade received by the customer</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Grade ordered: Premium</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Grade ordered: Excellent</strong></span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Grade ordered: Good</strong></span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Excellent</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Good</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">10% of the product sale price</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">5% of the product sale price</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Fair</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">15% of the product sale price</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">10% of the product sale price</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">5% of the product sale price</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div style=\"left: 20px;top: 640.065px;\"> </div>\n<div style=\"left: 20px;top: 640.065px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">In case of the dirty item or item worse than fair, the Agent may propose 5% commercial gesture.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The minimum commercial gesture is 5 EUR/GBP/USD. To increase the probability that the customer will keep the device, for all partial refunds or goodwill gestures, the amount will be rounded up to the nearest 5€ or $5. For example, a refund of 7€ will be rounded up to 10€. This does not apply to partial refunds for late express shipping, which will be refunded at the exact shipping cost.</span></div>"
}